      |                 | "double" quotes |
      |                 | question?       |
      |                 | &and#hash       |
    And the user deletes the following file using the webUI
      | name-parts      |
      | 'single'        |
      | "double" quotes |
      | question?       |
      | &and#hash       |
    Then the following file should be listed in the trashbin on the webUI
      | name-parts      |
      | 'single'        |
      | "double" quotes |
      | question?       |
      | &and#hash       |

